SELF JION to find employee-manager pairs.

Table: employees (employee_id, name, manager_id)

SELECT e1.employee_id AS employee, e2.manager_id AS manager
FROM employees e1
LEFT JOIN employees e2 ON e1.manager_id = e2.employee_id;

matching employee's manager id in e1 (employee table) with manager's employee id in e2 (manager table).
